channel.title: Looking For Future Bass Collborator
channel.description: Hey everyone! I’m currently having some cravings for some Future Bass. I’m looking to change things up a bit from my norm, and I’ve heard some amazing FB on this forum, so I think this would be a great little project. If anyone would be willing to work on something, PM me and we could work something out! Thanks everyone, and have an awesome holiday!
